# 🗺️ StudyBot: Complete Design Diagrams

This document contains a series of diagrams to help you understand every aspect of the platform's infrastructure and data flow.

---

## 1. 🏗️ High-Level System Architecture
**Purpose:** Showing how the frontend, API, and services connect.

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Client ["Client (Next.js Frontend)"]
        User(["👤 User"])
        Sidebar["Sidebar Component"]
        ChatPage["Chat Section (Doubt)"]
        NotesPage["Notes Section"]
    end

    subgraph API ["API Layer (tRPC)"]
        TRPC["tRPC Middleware / Procedures"]
        AuthRouter["Auth Router"]
        NoteRouter["Note Router"]
        DoubtRouter["Doubt Router"]
        TimetableRouter["Timetable Router"]
    end

    subgraph Services ["External Services"]
        Prisma["Prisma ORM"]
        DB[("PostgreSQL Database")]
        Groq["Groq AI (Llama 3)"]
    end

    User --> Sidebar
    User --> ChatPage
    
    ChatPage == "Queries/Mutations" ==> TRPC
    TRPC --- DoubtRouter
    
    DoubtRouter --> Groq
    DoubtRouter --> Prisma
    Prisma --> DB
```

