## 3. 💬 Sequence Diagram: Asking a Doubt
**Purpose:** Showing the step-by-step lifecycle of an AI request.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant TRPC as tRPC Router
    participant Groq as Groq AI API
    participant DB as Database (Prisma)

    User->>Frontend: Types doubt and clicks "Send"
    Frontend->>DB: Saves user message in chat history
    Frontend->>TRPC: Calls doubtRouter.sendMessage()
    
    TRPC->>DB: Fetches recent history for context
    TRPC->>Groq: Sends user doubt + history context
    Groq-->>TRPC: Returns Llama 3 AI response
    
    TRPC->>DB: Saves AI message in chat history
    TRPC-->>Frontend: Sends back the AI response
    Frontend-->>User: Renders the AI response bubble
```

