## 4. 📝 State Diagram: Study Session Lifecycle
**Purpose:** Visualizing the user journey from login to studying.

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unauthenticated
    Unauthenticated --> Authenticated : Sign In / Sign Up
    
    state Authenticated {
        [*] --> Dashboard
        Dashboard --> Chatting : "Ask a Doubt"
        Chatting --> Dashboard : Close Chat
        
        Dashboard --> TakingNotes : "Create / Edit Note"
        TakingNotes --> AIReview : "Summarize with AI"
        AIReview --> TakingNotes
        
        Dashboard --> ExamPrep : "Set Exam Date"
        ExamPrep --> Practice : "Generate AI Questions"
    }
    
    Authenticated --> Unauthenticated : Sign Out
    Unauthenticated --> [*]
```

